real-time.subtitle: Turjun inta u dhaxaysa 40+ luqadaha saxeexan iyo kuwa lagu hadlo wakhtiga dhabta ah
real-time.description: Abkayagu waxa uu kuu ogolaanayaa inaad si dabiici ah oo fudud ula xidhiidho qof kasta, meel kasta, wakhti kasta, luuqadaada dhegoolaha.

multilingual.title: Taageerada luuqadaha badan
multilingual.subtitle: Utarjum inta u dhaxaysa luqadaha dhegoolaha ee kala duwan iyo luqadaha lagu hadlo
multilingual.description: App-kayagu waxa uu taageeraa luuqado badan oo dhegooleyaal ah iyo luqado lagu hadlo, si aad ula xidhiidho dadka ka yimid dalal iyo dhaqamo kala duwan.

appearance.title: Muuqaal la beddeli karo
appearance.subtitle: Sawirkayaga dhabta ah ee luqada dhegoolaha avatars-ka ayaa bixiya xulashooyin badan oo kala duwan oo lagu habeynayo si ay ugu habboonaato baahiyahaaga gaarka ah.
appearance.description: Haddii aad rabto inaad abuurto avatar adiga kuu eg ama aad abuurto dabeecad gaar ah, xulashooyinkayada habaynta waxay kuu oggolaanayaan inaad naftaada u muujiso hab adiga kugu habboon oo run ah.

open-source.title: Mashruuca Isha Furan
open-source.subtitle: Saxiix Translate waa mashruuc il furan, oo u oggolaanaya bulshada inay wax ku biiriyaan oo ay kor u qaadaan sifooyinkooda.
open-source.description: Markaan wadaagno koodka isha, waxaan hiigsaneynaa inaan kobcino wadashaqeyn iyo daahfurnaan.

offline.title: Waxqabadka khadka tooska ah
offline.subtitle: Saxiix shaqada Turjumaada meel kasta, xitaa khadka tooska ah ee diyaaradda.
offline.description: Haddi aad ku safrayso, meel fog, ama internet la'aanteed, abkayagu waxa uu hubinayaa in aad mar walba u turjumi karto luqadda lagu hadlo ama qoran luqadda dhegoolaha, adiga oo farahaaga ku haynaya qalabka isgaarsiinta muhiimka ah.
